    org.apache.bcel.generic.Visitor

    public class MetricMethodVisitor
extends org.apache.bcel.generic.EmptyVisitor
    The simplest of method visitors, prints any invoked method signature for all method invocations. Class copied with modifications from CJKM: http://www.spinellis.gr/sw/ckjm/
